     * Creates a new {@code PricingSessionWindow} for the specified market.
     *
     * @param marketId The identifier for the market (e.g., "NYSE", "LSE")
     * @param timezone The timezone in which the market operates
     * @param sessionOpen The market open time in local time
     * @param sessionClose The market close time in local time
     * @return The pricing session window assigner
